title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1980-12-31
description:
Set I
Acoustic Set

Dire Wolf
On The Road Again
To Lay Me Down
Monkey & The Engineer
Jack-A-Roe
Cassidy
I've Been All Around This World
The Race Is On
Bird Song >
Ripple
Set II
Electric Set 1

Alabama Getaway >
Greatest Story Ever Told
They Love Each Other
Little Red Rooster *
China Cat Sunflower >
I Know You Rider
Looks Like Rain
Althea
Lost Sailor >
Saint Of Circumstance >
Deal
Set III
Electric Set 2

New Years Countdown >
Sugar Magnolia >
Scarlet Begonias >
Fire On The Mountain $
Estimated Prophet >
Drums >
Space >
The Other One >
Wharf Rat > $
Around & Around > $
Sunshine Daydream $

Encore:
(I Can't Get No) Satisfaction >
Brokedown Palace
Comment
Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
Matthew Kelly - Harmonica *
John Cipollina - Guitar $
